<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mortally" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mortally,</orth> 1) in the manner of mortal men: <cit><quote>I was m. brought forth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 5.1.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. V, 1, 105</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) to death, irrecoverably: <cit><quote>some m., some lightly touched,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.3.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 3, 10</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>they hurt you m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 3.3.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 3, 6</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>